        "CLOSED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，已填充和草稿都能归档。最后归档状态要落到群件维基页面做记录，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
